flowchart TD
  A[Plan a questionnaire change] --> B{What kind of change is it?}
  B -->|Wording or translation| C[Keep the same item_id]
  B -->|Response logic or options| D[Review required fields, q0/q1 dose triplets, and ordering]
  B -->|Scorable item or factor change| E[Review canonical scale_id coverage and create a new dated version]

  C --> F[Edit one stacked multi-language questionnaire table]
  D --> F
  E --> F

  G[English rows define structure] --> F
  H[Translation rows focus on wording] --> F
  O[randomize_question_order lives on the English q0 row] --> F

  F --> I[Create or update the dated Google Sheets tab]
  I --> J[Loader trims separators and validates the table]
  J --> K[Definition hash is computed from the loaded version]
  K --> L[Participant language selects the runtime view]
  L --> M[Validate one full submit path and feedback render]
  M --> N[Open the running survey once if you want to confirm the latest sheet version]
